Then Kutcher's character falls in love with Kate Hudson as she sees her walk out of the pool at the Caesar hotel and she has NO IDEA that Kutcher and Whalberg are con artists but Kutcher's character is certain he wants to marry and elope with Hudson's character. But WAIT! George Clooney plays an undercover suave cop along side Pierce Brosnan, the salt and pepper haired antagonists and Clooney is totally having a thing with Hudson's character but Hudson grows feelings for Kutcher's character. The movie would be called something like -- "Aces and Spades" but this, this is far more basic than I can ever imagine.

Unknowingly, many times we all hurt our mother. Today we all apologize to our mother here and wish her a long life.
